OL,3,CJohn Swinney sworn in as Scotland's
OL,4,Cnew first minister
OL,6,FJohn Swinney has officially been sworn
OL,7,Fin as Scotland's new first minister at
OL,8,Fthe Court of Session in Edinburgh.
OL,10,FIt comes after the Perthshire North
OL,11,FMSP was on Monday following the
OL,12,Fresignation of Humza Yousaf.
OL,14,FMr Swinney, who has previously served
OL,15,Fas finance secretary, education
OL,16,Fsecretary and deputy first minister
OL,17,Ffor the Scottish government, is
OL,18,Fexpected to appoint his new cabinet
OL,19,Flater today.
