OL,3,CJohn Swinney sworn in as Scotland's
OL,4,Cnew first minister
OL,6,FKate Forbes, who was widely touted as
OL,7,Fa successor to Mr Yousaf , is expected
OL,8,Fto be given a cabinet role.
OL,10,FScotland's most senior judge, the Lord
OL,11,FPresident Lord Carloway, presided over
OL,12,Fthis morning's ceremony, which saw the
OL,13,Fnew leader make his statutory
OL,14,Fdeclaration.
OL,16,FMr Swinney raised his right hand and
OL,17,Fbowed his head as Lord Carloway read
OL,18,Fthe three oaths of office ` for the
OL,19,Frole of first minister, the Keeper of
OL,20,Fthe Great Seal and the oath of
OL,21,Fallegiance to the King.
