OL,6,FThe Lord President then addressed the
OL,7,Fcourt about the independence of the
OL,8,Fjudiciary.
OL,10,FMr Swinney takes on the role at a
OL,11,Fparticularly chaotic time for the SNP,
OL,12,Fwith Mr Yousaf ending his party's
OL,13,Fpowersharing agreement with the
OL,14,FScottish Greens in a row over climate
OL,15,Ftargets and gender reforms.
