OL,4,Cnew first minister
OL,6,FThe move triggered an expected no
OL,7,Fconfidence vote in Mr Yousaf's
OL,8,Fleadership, but he stood down before
OL,9,Fit could be held. T, but the whole
OL,10,Fsaga has still a reflection of the
OL,11,Flevel of turbulence within the SNP.
OL,13,FMeanwhile the husband of former first
OL,14,Fminister Nicola Sturgeon, former SNP
OL,15,Fchief executive Peter Murrell, is
OL,17,FMr Swinney, who was SNP leader between
OL,18,F2000 and 2004, will now have the task
OL,19,Fof restoring unity and calm to
OL,20,FScotland's ruling party.
