OL,3,CJohn Swinney sworn in as Scotland's
OL,4,Cnew first minister
OL,6,FThe new first minister was accompanied
OL,7,Fby his family, including wife
OL,8,FElizabeth, 13-year-old son Matthew and
OL,9,Fbrother David at today's ceremony.
OL,11,FSpeaking to reporters after the
OL,12,Fceremony, Mr Swinney said taking the
OL,13,Foaths had been an "overwhelming
OL,14,Fmoment" and he spoke of his pride at
OL,15,Fbeing first minister and his family's
OL,16,Fsupport.
